{"tid":87746,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]仁王 最終體驗版 DEMO 48小時限定 (21,22星期六日)","createTime":"2017-01-20T05:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T13:44:17.000Z","uid":68446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7180c95bc5aeb25ae0fca91f6c7a438c8e473594","tid":87746,"uid":68446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/final_top.jpg?resize=700%2C600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Ffinal_top.jpg%3Fresize%3D700%252C600&h=c6883a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《仁王》將於2月9日推出，而光榮就宣佈會於1月21日凌晨發佈「最終體驗版」！而今次將會比之前兩天的配佈時間還要短，只有48小時！<br />\n<br />\n在1月21日0時至1月22日23時59分內，完成「二俣」關卡中的「彼岸への思い」(通往彼岸的思念)，就可以得到在正式版可使用的裝備「女鬼之面」以及道具「女鬼之面製法書」，另外，之前錯過「&alpha;體驗版」及「&beta;體驗版」的玩家也可以在此體驗版中藉由取得「制霸之証」及「強者之証」來得到正式版可使用的裝備「怨靈鬼兜」以及「飛緣魔兜」！想把以上道具得到的玩家，就不要錯過此次體驗版了！另外注意本試玩版遊玩時必須保時在連線狀態，否則會強制終止。還有就是必須保留完成以上行動的存檔才能得到以上道具哦。<br />\n<br />\n女鬼之面<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/656fb444d1ca3e62d6d4821c059f2837_tb.jpg?resize=500%2C859\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F656fb444d1ca3e62d6d4821c059f2837_tb.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C859&h=a592c7e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛緣魔兜<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/d7833dee037ddc47c47fd96909f96931_tb.jpg?resize=800%2C800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fd7833dee037ddc47c47fd96909f96931_tb.jpg%3Fresize%3D800%252C800&h=a5c22df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怨靈鬼兜<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/d7833dee037ddc47c47fd96909f96931_tb.jpg?resize=800%2C800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.